[Student "S"]
{NORTH has both Majors and enough points to open 2\C. 
SOUTH, with 4 points, responds with a negative 2\D.

NORTH first bids her higher ranking suit, 2\S. 
SOUTH is too strong for second negative, he bids 2NT.

NORTH now shows her second suit, 3\H.

SOUTH is happy to bid the game in \Hs.}

