[SkillPath "partnership_bidding/two_club"]
[Student "S"]
{NORTH, with 9 points and a 5-card suit, should make a positive response, 2\S.

SOUTH bids her \Hs and NORTH agrees the trump suit with a 
4\H bid.

SOUTH thinks there is a slam, so she invokes Blackwood. Hearing that NORTH holds two Aces she bids 
6NT. She could also have bid 6\H but 6NT scores a little more.}

